Received Ilsa Tigress Of Siberia promptly and in excellent condition. Picture quality and tracking is excellent, nice to see Ilsa at it again.

Not a strong movie in the Ilsa family, the production cost of this movie is clearly high.  It has everything from chase scenes, to hidden cameras and even computers!  It is filmed in different locations and uses a larger cast. But it is a sexploiation film and it fails at that.  Not enough nudity, sex, and exploitation!

This is a classic cult film from the Ilsa series starring Dyanne Thorne. She is a ruthless warden of a Siberian prison camp. If the cold is not enough for you. She'll be so wicked you'd rather be in hell. Don't forget to see her other films, Ilsa she wolf of the SS, Ilsa harem keeper of the oil sheiks, and Ilsa the wicked warden. If you are a cult film collector these are must have films. You won't be disappointed.
